ask's output contract\n143\t * to the harness state file. Only runs for tasks named 'implement' whose\n144\t * output contract contains a non-null `testResults`.\n145\t *\n146\t * This sets `session_flags.tests_passed` and `session_flags.coverage_met`\n147\t * before the verify task runs, so verify's precondition check passes\n148\t * without re-running coverage.\n149\t */"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ddtfy6XmQWtkAycqZdji9G","session_id":"b6bb3bfc-8778-4f16-a616-88028acc2431","uuid":"b317f391-1618-467f-8ea9-17fdbbc940e5","timestamp":"2026-04-03T18:40:59.721Z"}
